title: Two Little Knights of Kentucky
creator: Annie Fellows Johnston
description: LibriVox recording of Two Little Knights of Kentucky, by Annie Fellows Johnston. In this volume the Little Colonel returns to us like an old friend, but with added grace and charm. She is not, however, the central figure of the story, that place being taken by the “two little knights,” Malcolm and Keith, little Southern aristocrats, whose chivalrous natures lead them through a series of interesting adventures. (Summary from an original 1898 advertisement for the book.) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
subject: librivox; audioook; children; fellows johnston; johnston; little colonel; Malcolm; Keith; two little knights; kentucky; children
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text

reviews.reviewbody: chapters 7 and 8 are not even read in English. They need to be redone. Ruins the entire book. Ask om to stick to reading in his own languages. Completely ruined the experience.
